videos.description: Here is a fast and easy tutorial on how to install Air Shou, an app for screen recording in iOS for iPhone, ipod touch, ipad and iPad PRO. This App allows you to record in multiple formats 720p, 1080p and records your voice. This is all done locally on your device.This does not require any jailbreak or hacks, just install the APP and you're good to go.Here is a short transcript of the tutorial:Firstly you need to go to your web browser, I have tested both google chrome and Safari so it should work with just about anything.Secondly do a search and type in ‘iEmulators’ when the page loads you should be greeted with the iEmulators website along with the sub catagory of ‘Air Shou’Click on it and you will be taken to the download page. Click here to install the App. A message will pop up, click ‘install’ and the download will begin.Before you begin using the app go to your settings, then general, then device management.Click trust and you can now enjoy your new screen recorder.Once you open the app just follow the prompts to get everything set up..
videos.title: How To Record POKÉMON GO on iOS / iPhone FREE & EASY!
